Product.create(Name:"Harry Potter and the Order of the Phoenix", Description:"You are sharing the Dark Lord's thoughts and emotions. The Headmaster thinks it inadvisable for this to continue. He wishes me to teach you how to close your mind to the Dark Lord.Dark times have come to Hogwarts. After the Dementors' attack on his cousin Dudley, Harry Potter knows that Voldemort will stop at nothing to find him. There are many who deny the Dark Lord's return, but Harry is not alone: a secret order gathers at Grimmauld Place to fight against the dark forces. ", image:'./assets/Harry Potter and the Order of the Phoenix.jpg', Price: 7.79)

Product.create(Name:"Harry Potter and the Goblet of Fire", Description:"Harry Potter wants to get away from the pernicious Dursleys and go to the International Quidditch Cup with Hermione, Ron, and the Weasleys. He wants to dream about Cho Chang, his crush (and maybe do more than dream). He wants to find out about the mysterious event involving two other rival schools of magic, and a competition that hasn't happened for a hundred years. He wants to be a normal, fourteen-year-old wizard. Unfortunately for Harry Potter, he's not normal - even by wizarding standards. And in this case, different can be deadly.", image:'./assets/Harry Potter and the Goblet of Fire.jpg', Price: 28.79)

Product.create(Name:"Harry Potter and the sorcerer Stone", Description:"A global phenomenon and cornerstone of contemporary children's literature, J.K. Rowling's Harry Potter series is both universally adored and critically acclaimed. Now, experience the magic as you've never heard it before. The inimitable Jim Dale brings to life an entire cast of characters-from the pinched, nasal whine of Petunia Dursley to the shrill huff of the Sorting Hat to the earnest, wondrous voice of the boy wizard himself.Orphaned as an infant, young Harry Potter has been living a less-than-fortunate life. Belittled by his pompous uncle and sniveling aunt (not to mention his absolute terror of a cousin, Dudley), Harry has resigned himself to a mediocre existence in the cupboard under the stairs. ", image:"./assets/Harry Potter and the sorcerer's Stone.jpg", Price: 11.99)

Product.create(Name:"Harry Potter and the Chamer of secrets", Description:"There is a plot, Harry Potter. A plot to make most terrible things happen at Hogwarts School of Witchcraft and Wizardry this year.Harry Potter's summer has included the worst birthday ever, doomy warnings from a house-elf called Dobby, and rescue from the Dursleys by his friend Ron Weasley in a magical flying car! Back at Hogwarts School of Witchcraft and Wizardry for his second year, Harry hears strange whispers echo through empty corridors - and then the attacks start. Students are found as though turned to stone... ", image:'./assets/Harry Potter and the Chamer of secrets.jpg', Price: 16.59)


